<h1>Weekly Horoscopes</h1>
<div class="subtitle">April 28–May 4 · Sayari Moon Astrology</div>

<p>
The week starts with Venus in Gemini trining Pluto in Aquarius, drawing you toward connections and information that feel empowering, strategic, or alluring. Conversations have depth, and curiosity can uncover something useful if you’re paying attention. Flattery will get you everywhere now. The following day, Venus square the North Node exposes which fleeting feelings, no matter how tempting, aren’t aligned with where you’re truly meant to go.
</p>

<p>
On Friday, the Full Moon in Scorpio brings an emotional situation to a head. There is a quiet realization within a relationship, agreement, or dynamic that has subtly shifted over time. Tension builds in silence, making it harder to maintain a neutral demeanor. This lunation highlights where power, control, or emotional investment have been out of balance, prompting a necessary release. Mercury is also conjunct Chiron in Aries, reinforcing that avoidance won’t resolve this—directness will.
</p>

<p>
On Saturday, Mercury enters Taurus, turning attention to more practical matters. It’s a key time for bringing more comfort in the home, grounding in the body, and building security all around.
</p>

